NumericalParametrized<T>
public interface Parametrized<T extends Parametrized<T,P>,P>
An object which has a modifiable parameter of type P.

    • withParams

      default T withParams(P param)
      Returns this object with the parameter reset to the provided value. Internally calls setParams(Object) and then returns this. Useful for adopting the chain invocation.
      Parameters:
      param - the new parameter value
      Returns:
      this object after having set the parameter value`
